# ECP Client Project Structure

## Main App Files

- [ecp_clientApp.swift](mdc:ecp-client/ecp_clientApp.swift) - Main app entry point
- [ContentView.swift](mdc:ecp-client/ContentView.swift) - Primary content view with comment list

## Comment System Components

- [CommentRowView.swift](mdc:ecp-client/CommentRowView.swift) - Individual comment display
- [ComposeCommentView.swift](mdc:ecp-client/ComposeCommentView.swift) - Comment creation interface
- [RepliesView.swift](mdc:ecp-client/RepliesView.swift) - Replies modal view

## Content Parsing & Display

- [ContentParser.swift](mdc:ecp-client/ContentParser.swift) - Content parsing logic for addresses, tokens, URLs
- [ParsedContentView.swift](mdc:ecp-client/ParsedContentView.swift) - Parsed content display with clickable elements

## UI Components

- [BlockiesAvatarView.swift](mdc:ecp-client/BlockiesAvatarView.swift) - Avatar component with blockies generation
- [ReferenceChip.swift](mdc:ecp-client/ReferenceChip.swift) - Reference chips for links, tokens, etc.
- [CommentSkeletonView.swift](mdc:ecp-client/CommentSkeletonView.swift) - Loading skeleton with shimmer effect
- [UserDetailView.swift](mdc:ecp-client/UserDetailView.swift) - User profile detail view

## Utilities

- [Blockies.swift](mdc:ecp-client/Blockies.swift) - Blockies generation for Ethereum addresses

## Assets

- [Assets.xcassets](mdc:ecp-client/Assets.xcassets) - App icons and colors
- [Preview Content](mdc:ecp-client/Preview Content) - SwiftUI preview assets

## Architecture Notes

- Follows SwiftUI best practices with separated concerns
- Uses `@StateObject` for observable services
- Implements proper state management with `@State`, `@ObservedObject`
- Components are modular and reusable
- Supports both light and dark mode with `@Environment(\.colorScheme)`
